=== Kernel ===

Pre-requisites:

Cross tools for ARM:
gcc-3.4.2
uClibc-0.9.27

I need to change the EXTRAVERSION in kernel Makefile to _mvlcee30-mainstone instead of _pnail. Otherwise there are problems with self compiled kernel modules.

Steps:
Download the [http://www.motorolafans.com/index.php?name=Downloads&file=details&id=197 patch] for [http://sourceforge.net/projects/e680 kernel] from download->E680i/A780->scripts/programs section 

gzip -cd patch-2.4.17-pnail-0.1.gz | patch -p0<br>
cd linux-2.4.17<br>
cp arch/arm/def-configs/ezx-780 .config<br>
make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux- oldconfig<br>
make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux- dep<br>
make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux- zImage<br>
make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux- modules<br>

